org.hms.entities

Packages that use org.hms.entities
Package
Description
org.hms
This package contains the main classes for the Hospital Management System (HMS).
org.hms.entities
This package contains the entity classes for the Hospital Management System (HMS).
org.hms.services.authentication
This package contains classes and interfaces for handling authentication services.
org.hms.services.drugdispensary
Provides services related to drug dispensary within the hospital management system.
org.hms.services.medicalrecord
Provides services related to medical records.
org.hms.services.staffmanagement
This package contains the staff management service classes for the Hospital Management System (HMS).
org.hms.views
This package contains the view classes for the Hospital Management System (HMS).
